# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Saiba Mais"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Estamos trabalhando arduamente para expandir este guia do usuário e melhorar "
"o OpenShot Video Editor, mas se você estiver com dificuldades e não souber "
"aonde recorrer, o OpenShot oferece várias fontes de informação adicional."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"O OpenShot possui vários `Tutoriais no YouTube <https://www.youtube.com/"
"playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ disponíveis para ajudar "
"você a aprender mais."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"O OpenShot possui uma `Comunidade de Usuários no Reddit <https://openshot."
"org/forum>`_ dedicada a usuários ajudando usuários, respondendo perguntas e "
"discutindo edição de vídeo e tópicos do OpenShot."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Se você gostaria de ajudar a melhorar este Guia do Usuário, `veja o código-"
"fonte no GitHub <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Se você descobriu um novo erro, por favor `Reporte um Bug <https://www."
"openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Se você precisar de suporte profissional, pode abrir um chamado enviando uma "
"mensagem para support@openshot.org ou `Agendar uma chamada <https://calendly."
"com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
